      "rationale": "NIH is the direct regulatory QoI and was used consistently in both validation and COU prediction. However, the validation dataset does not span the full range of hematocrit values anticipated in the clinical population, leaving a residual gap at level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
