      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Inlet boundary conditions in CFD match measured experimental inlet conditions within 5%; any deviations quantified and their effect on QoI bounded.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity magnitude matched within 3% of measured values. Inlet turbulence intensity was assumed at 5% in CFD; experimental turbulence intensity was not measured, introducing an unquantified discrepancy. This prevents achievement of level 4."
